Package: bulmages
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, bulmages-common (>= 0.11)
Recommends: bulmages-server-admin (>= 0.11), bulmacont (>= 0.11), bulmafact (>= 0.11)
Description: Accounting and invoicing programs for Spanish SMEes
 This package provides the entire Bulmages financial suite for Spanish
 SMEs.  Bulmages includes an accounting program (bulmacont), an invoicing
 program (bulmafact), administration programs, and documentation.
 .
 This program is made in an open community, you are welcome to join us.

Package: bulmages-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kpdf | okular | evince, python
Recommends: python-uniconvertor (>= 1.1.3)
Description: Bulmages invoicing and accounting, config and common stuff
 The config file bulmages.conf for all the bulmages programs.

